data.description: Cute starter home featuring split plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, covered patio, granite counter tops and nice owner's suite with walk-in closet.   This home is in great condition and built in 2018.  You will be delighted with the kitchen bar and spacious open floor plan. No HOA and a lot that gives you space.
